{"tid":577733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習權風暴】「敏感詞」越加越多！「吾皇萬歲」「N」「《1984》」都唔得","createTime":"2018-03-02T04:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T16:11:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e4fb2de987e08e9d55e093fcba747f6b15574df7","tid":577733,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180302/large/1519957021_6775.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180302%2Flarge%2F1519957021_6775.jpg&h=858c0e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共早前宣佈修憲建議，刪除國家主席任期限制，國家主席意味習近平有可能終身掌權，引發社會輿論，網上聲音更是擋不住。早前，有網民發現，中國當局封殺了「袁世凱」、「稱帝」、「司馬昭之心」；「小熊維民」、安全套品牌「杜蕾斯」等諷刺性的關鍵詞和言論，昨有內地媒體報道，「敏感詞」越增越多。<br />\n<br />\n內地網民「美娟美心」將官方修憲報道的截圖，上面寫了個「吾皇萬歲萬萬歲」，結果沒法成功發文。她說：「我有3個號（微博帳號），我一個號發完以後，就用另一個號去看，很長時間沒有（被人）點讚，那肯定就是屏蔽了。它（當局）也知道這些會招來民間的譏諷和反對，它要把這些都屏蔽掉」。<br />\n<br />\n另有網民也發現，英文字母「N」一度無法搜索。有海外的漢學家推測，當局擔心市民以「N&gt;2」諷刺兩屆任期制，可能成為歷史。<br />\n<br />\n而由作家喬治.奧威爾（George Orwell）諷刺共產極權的著作《1984》和《動物農莊》（Animal Farm），在中國的網絡上也無法搜索。<br />\n<br />\n除了「吾皇」，其他被封殺的「敏感詞」多不勝數，包括「萬歲」、「登基」、「稱帝」、「主席」、「終身制」、「習澤東」、「袁世凱」、「復辟」、「黃袍加身」、甚至「小熊維尼」，源於這個動畫人物在中國微博上的金句：「找到一樣你所鐘愛的事物，然後永不放手」（Find the thing you love and stick with it）<br />\n<br />\n上海網民馬小姐認為，當局機關算盡，卻高估了老百姓對修憲的關注，「他們（當權者）要想幹甚麼就一定會把它幹成，老百姓想要反對甚麼一定是不成功的。現在有幾種封鎖，一是封鎖關鍵詞，又或乾脆封鎖某些人，到後來它們就直接封鎖你個人的文章，你無論到甚麼地方去發都沒用。尤其像我們經常在網上發表觀點的人，肯定就是它們關注的重點。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180302/57893552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180302%2F57893552&d=VsVLdbPc2yurNKMoUaw2rgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=96e360bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180302%2F57893552&h=6e70aff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180302/57893552</a>"},{"pid":"caefe0440ada7d334ecba62869e01fca971f13f3","tid":577733,"uid":48139,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">甚至「小熊維尼」，源於這個動畫人物在中國微博上的金句：「找到一樣你所鐘愛的事物，然後永不放手」（Find the thing you love and stick with it）</span><br />\n<br />\n有呢句野之前已經叫維尼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b70eaa81dea0fdc2b144589f5e490dbadce7df4","tid":577733,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"吾皇james 咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573ba50c6ec9cfb8cc794d0d79f43c7527dd589b","tid":577733,"uid":54337,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:47:20.000Z","msg":"登基唔得，試下燉雞"},{"pid":"6c9c3feb392e0e48ee184212cc39f2979b42b497","tid":577733,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b70eaa81dea0fdc2b144589f5e490dbadce7df4","tid":577733,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"吾皇james 咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"等被封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe837c352d790d285adac92b03f07cf09747eab3","tid":577733,"uid":78620,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"中國個search engine就黎search唔到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13a4dbb80fc6cfa4596db953fdb021b25e50b31","tid":577733,"uid":25556,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"幾時肅清1984